        <mxCell id="recipe_label" value="Image Recipe: golden-win2022-recipe&#10;Base: windows-server-2022-english-full-base-x86/x.x.x (always latest)&#10;Block device: 50 GB gp3, KMS-encrypted, delete-on-termination&#10;lifecycle.create_before_destroy = true (immutable versioning)&#10;&#10;   Build components (run sequentially in ONE instance):&#10;   ┌──── 1. windows-updates (v1.0.2)   — install latest Windows patches&#10;   ├──── 2. cis-hardening  (v1.0.2)    — apply CIS Benchmark baseline&#10;   └──── 3. agent-install  (v1.0.2)    — install SSM Agent + CloudWatch Agent&#10;&#10;   Test component (runs in SEPARATE instance after build):&#10;   └──── 4. validation-test (v1.0.2)  — Pester validation suite"
                style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;fillColor=#FFF8E7;strokeColor=#ED7100;dashed=0;fontColor=#232F3E;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=4;"
