        <mxCell id="ec2_label" value="Build / Test EC2 Instance (transient)&#10;&#10;═══ PHASE 1: BUILD (one instance) ═══&#10;• Windows Server 2022 base AMI&#10;• t3.medium / t3.large&#10;• Instance Profile: golden-win2022-imagebuilder-profile&#10;• terminate_instance_on_failure = true&#10;&#10;Sequential execution:&#10;  [1] windows-updates  → ✔ patched&#10;  [2] cis-hardening    → ✔ hardened&#10;  [3] agent-install    → ✔ SSM Agent + CloudWatch Agent&#10;  [4] sysprep / snapshot → ✔ AMI captured&#10;&#10;═══ PHASE 2: TEST (separate instance) ═══&#10;• Launched from the AMI just built&#10;• Runs Pester validation-test component&#10;• Tests agents, services, hardening state&#10;• Pass/fail gates pipeline → AVAILABLE/FAILED"
                style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;fillColor=#FFF0E5;strokeColor=#ED7100;fontColor=#232F3E;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=4;"
