        <mxCell id="lambda_label" value="Lambda: golden-win2022-update-ssm-param&#10;&#10;Runtime: Python 3.12 | Timeout: 30 s&#10;Env vars: SSM_PARAMETER_NAME, SNS_TOPIC_ARN&#10;&#10;On AVAILABLE:&#10;  1. imagebuilder:GetImage → new AMI ID&#10;  2. ssm:PutParameter → /golden-images/.../latest-ami-id&#10;  3. sns:Publish → notify team/Slack&#10;&#10;IAM: least-privilege (SSM, imagebuilder, SNS, CW Logs)"
                style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#7155ED;fontColor=#232F3E;spacingLeft=6;spacingTop=4;"
